{
  "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "平面上散布着一堆点，我们想把它们连成一张三角网。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.28,
      "size": 36432,
      "text": "连法千千万，可网格有好有坏，瘦长的三角形最让人头疼。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "有没有一种连法，天生就是最优的？答案就是 Delaunay 三角剖分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "circle",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "circle-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/circle-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "它的标志是一条黄金法则：每个三角形的外接圆内，不含任何其他点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "circle",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "circle-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/circle-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "这就是空圆性质，画面里那个粉色的圆，圈住三个顶点却空无一物。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "circle",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "circle-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/circle-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.68,
      "size": 42912,
      "text": "增量算法正是靠它:插入新点时,凡外接圆包住它的三角形都要重连。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "angle",
      "line_id": "ang-1",
      "filename": "angle-ang-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/angle-ang-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "空圆性质带来一个漂亮的后果:它让所有三角形里的最小角尽可能大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "angle",
      "line_id": "ang-2",
      "filename": "angle-ang-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/angle-ang-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "换句话说,它极力避免又瘦又尖的三角形,让网格更接近正三角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "angle",
      "line_id": "ang-3",
      "filename": "angle-ang-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/angle-ang-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "这种匀称,正是数值计算和渲染最喜欢的形状。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "dual",
      "line_id": "dual-1",
      "filename": "dual-dual-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/dual-dual-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "把每个三角形的外接圆心连起来,就得到了沃罗诺伊图。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "dual",
      "line_id": "dual-2",
      "filename": "dual-dual-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/dual-dual-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.59,
      "size": 41472,
      "text": "两者互为对偶:一个管三角连边,一个管领地划分,是同一枚硬币的两面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "调整点的数量,看三角网如何从稀疏变得密实。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "点开外接圆,亲眼验证每个圆内部都干干净净。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "Delaunay 三角剖分用空圆性质,连出一张最优的三角网。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "它最大化最小角,又与沃罗诺伊图完美对偶。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "delaunay-triangulation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/delaunay-triangulation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "一条简单的空圆法则,撑起了整个计算几何,我们下次再见!"
    }
  ],
